{
  "texts": [
    "One may limit word count, style, or the intended kind of response.",
    "\"Respond in fewer than 100 words in a professional tone\" commands a clear limit that improves the output quality of the model.",
    "One of the main determinants of designing prompts is whether to offer simple instructions or examples.",
    "For basic or routine chores like writing a greeting, directions can be more sufficient.",
    "For more complex or specialized jobs, though such as creating compliance language for banking application illustrative examples help."
  ]
}